# Cross Subsystem Invariants

## Must
- Keep one material translation source of truth across simulation/render/audio.
- Ensure audio events reference valid snapshot timeline IDs.
- Ensure surrogates carry `truth_reference_id` and traceability metadata.
- Keep event ordering and ID mapping stable across subsystem boundaries.

## Must Not
- Do not introduce parallel translators that reinterpret material state independently.
- Do not emit cross-subsystem artifacts with missing lineage metadata.

## Required Evidence
- Cross-subsystem consistency check output in CI artifacts.
